   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Fourier basis"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "4e783d6f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "We now want to move to the fourier basis, because I kinda need to understand how that works."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "17cb083b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
